+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:2001
+msgid "Should /usr/sbin/hddtemp be installed SUID root?"
+msgstr "MГЎ se /usr/sbin/hddtemp nainstalovat jako SUID root?"
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:2001
+msgid ""
+"You have the option of installing hddtemp with the SUID bit set, allowing it "
+"to be run (reporting hard drive temperatures) by regular users and not only "
+"the superuser."
+msgstr ""
+"MГЎte moЕҫnost nainstalovat hddtemp s nastavenГҪm SUID bitem, coЕҫ znamenГЎ, Еҫe "
+"jej kromДӣ sprГЎvce budou moci spouЕЎtДӣt i bДӣЕҫnГӯ uЕҫivatelГ© (a zjiЕЎЕҘovat teplotu "
+"pevnГ©ho disku)."
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:2001
+msgid ""
+"This could potentially allow hddtemp to be used during an attack against the "
+"computer's security. If in doubt, do not choose this option."
+msgstr ""
+"Takto nastavenГҪ hddtemp mЕҜЕҫe bГҪt potenciГЎlnДӣ vyuЕҫit ke kompromitovГЎnГӯ "
+"poДҚГӯtaДҚe. Pokud si nejste jisti, pak je lepЕЎГӯ tuto moЕҫnost zamГӯtnout."
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:2001 ../templates:4001
+msgid ""
+"This setting can be modified later by running 'dpkg-reconfigure hddtemp'."
+msgstr "ZmДӣnГӯte-li pozdДӣji nГЎzor, staДҚГӯ spustit вҖһdpkg-reconfigure hddtempвҖң."
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:3001
+msgid "Interval between hard drive temperature checks:"
+msgstr "Interval mezi kontrolami teploty pevnГ©ho disku:"
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:3001
+msgid ""
+"The temperature of the hard drive(s) can be logged by hddtemp via the "
+"generic system logging interface."
+msgstr ""
+"hddtemp mЕҜЕҫe zaznamenГЎvat teplotu pevnГ©ho disku (pevnГҪch diskЕҜ) pЕҷes obecnГ© "
+"logovacГӯ rozhranГӯ systГ©mu."
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:3001
+msgid ""
+"Please enter a value in seconds corresponding to the interval between two "
+"checks. To disable this feature, enter 0."
+msgstr ""
+"Zadejte poДҚet sekund odpovГӯdajГӯcГӯ dobДӣ mezi po sobДӣ jdoucГӯmi mДӣЕҷenГӯmi. Pro "
+"zakГЎzГЎnГӯ tГ©to vlastnosti jednoduЕЎe zadejte 0."
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:4001
+msgid "Should the hddtemp daemon be started at boot?"
+msgstr "MГЎ se daemon hddtemp spouЕЎtДӣt pЕҷi startu poДҚГӯtaДҚe?"
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:4001
+msgid ""
+"The hddtemp program can be run as a daemon, listening on port 7634 for "
+"incoming connections. It is used by some software such as gkrellm to get the "
+"temperature of hard drives."
+msgstr ""
+"Program hddtemp mЕҜЕҫe bДӣЕҫet jako daemon a ДҚekat na portu 7634 na pЕҷГӯchozГӯ "
+"spojenГӯ. Takto mЕҜЕҫe bГҪt vyuЕҫГӯvГЎn programy typu gkrellm pro zjiЕЎtДӣnГӯ aktuГЎlnГӯ "
+"teploty pevnГҪch diskЕҜ."
+
+#. Type: boolean
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:4001
+msgid ""
+"You have the option of starting the hddtemp daemon automatically on system "
+"boot. If in doubt, it is suggested to not start it automatically on boot."
+msgstr ""
+"MГЎte moЕҫnost spouЕЎtДӣt daemona hddtemp automaticky pЕҷi startu systГ©mu. Pokud "
+"si nejste jisti, pak jej radДӣji pЕҷi startu systГ©mu nespouЕЎtДӣjte."
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:5001
+msgid "Interface to listen on:"
+msgstr "RozhranГӯ, na kterГ©m naslouchat:"
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:5001
+msgid ""
+"The hddtemp program can listen for incoming connections on a specific "
+"interface, or on all interfaces."
+msgstr ""
+"Program hddtemp mЕҜЕҫe oДҚekГЎvat pЕҷГӯchozГӯ spojenГӯ na konkrГ©tnГӯm rozhranГӯ nebo "
+"na vЕЎech rozhranГӯch."
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:5001
+msgid ""
+"To listen on a specific interface, enter the IP address of that interface  "
+"(choosing 127.0.0.1 will accept local connections only). To listen on all "
+"interfaces, enter 0.0.0.0."
+msgstr ""
+"Aby poslouchal na konkrГ©tnГӯm rozhranГӯ, zadejte IP adresu danГ©ho rozhranГӯ "
+"(127.0.0.1 znamenГЎ, Еҫe bude pЕҷijГӯmat pouze lokГЎlnГӯ spojenГӯ). Pokud chcete, "
+"aby poslouchal na vЕЎech rozhranГӯch, zadejte 0.0.0.0."
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:6001
+msgid "Port to listen on:"
+msgstr "Port, na kterГ©m naslouchat:"
+
+#. Type: string
+#. Description
+#: ../templates:6001
+msgid ""
+"By default, hddtemp listens for incoming connections on port 7634. This can "
+"be changed for another port number."
+msgstr ""
+"hddtemp standardnДӣ oДҚekГЎvГЎ pЕҷГӯchozГӯ spojenГӯ na portu 7634. Pokud vГЎm tento "
+"port nevyhovuje, mЕҜЕҫete zadat jinГҪ."
