+"  -v   --version     :  display hddtemp version number.\n"
+"  -w   --wake-up     :  wake-up the drive if need.\n"
+"  -4                 :  listen on IPv4 sockets only.\n"
+"  -6                 :  listen on IPv6 sockets only.\n"
+"\n"
+"Report bugs or new drives to <hddtemp@guzu.net>.\n"
+msgstr ""
